I don't know the whole story but i do know that gating on your group in the crypt is pretty much a death sentence, then couple that with doing it mid fight.  I would be interested in hearing what the circumstances were that he would gate.  Short of every group member telling him he needs to leave now, I don;t see too many possibilities for it being &quot;justified&quot;, be it one person in /tells telling him he is the biggest piece of shit or two, you just don;t gate on your group when you are the key.<br>
<br>
Bottomline if my group pissed me off while in the crypt, I would inform them that they need to make a straight line for the exit, or be short one chanter, but no warning.... bad judgement call.<br>
